Subject: Updated Driver for ADS Cadet Radio Card
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/1999/3/31/218

This patch adds support for the ADS Cadet radio card to 2.2.5.  In
addition to full support for both AM and FM tuners on the card, it now
offers greatly improved autodetection of the card.
More information on the card, along with plans for further future
development of the driver can be found at:
http://linux.blackhawke.net/cadet.html.
